  "title": "Enum PixelType",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType' id='Alis_Core_Graphic_OpenGL_Enums_PixelType'>Enum PixelType    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Graphic/src/OpenGL/Enums/PixelType.cs#L35'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.html'>Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pixel type enum</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public enum PixelType</code></pre><h2 class='section'>Fields</h2><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>Byte = 5120</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The byte pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedByte = 5121</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned byte pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Short = 5122</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The short pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedShort = 5123</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned short pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Int = 5124</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The int pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedInt = 5125</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned int pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Float = 5126</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The float pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>HalfFloat = 5131</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The half float pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Bitmap = 6656</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The bitmap pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedByte332 = 32818</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned byte 332 pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedByte332Ext = 32818</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned byte 332 ext pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedShort4444 = 32819</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned short 4444 pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedShort4444Ext = 32819</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned short 4444 ext pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedShort5551 = 32820</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned short 5551 pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedShort5551Ext = 32820</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned short 5551 ext pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedInt8888 = 32821</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned int 8888 pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedInt8888Ext = 32821</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned int 8888 ext pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedInt1010102 = 32822</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned int 1010102 pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedInt1010102Ext = 32822</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned int 1010102 ext pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedByte233Reversed = 33634</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned byte 233 reversed pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedShort565 = 33635</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned short 565 pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedShort565Reversed = 33636</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned short 565 reversed pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedShort4444Reversed = 33637</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned short 4444 reversed pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedShort1555Reversed = 33638</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned short 1555 reversed pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedInt8888Reversed = 33639</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned int 8888 reversed pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedInt2101010Reversed = 33640</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned int 2101010 reversed pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedInt248 = 34042</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned int 248 pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedInt10F11F11FRev = 35899</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned int 10 11 11 rev pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnsignedInt5999Rev = 35902</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unsigned int 5999 rev pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Float32UnsignedInt248Rev = 36269</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelType.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The float 32 unsigned int 248 rev pixel type</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
